Question: Each image contains one schnauzer with grayish body fur and lighter fur on its 'beard', and the dog on the left is sitting upright, while the dog on the right is standing on something elevated.

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the dog on the left sitting upright?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the dog on the right standing on something elevated?')

ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the dog on the right has grayish body fur and lighter fur on its "beard"?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
